data.comment: The match has started.
Hammarby have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 4, Free kick for Hammarby in their own half.
Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in for Hacken in their own half.
In the minute 7, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Hammarby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hammarby in their own half.
In the minute 9, Aimar Sher (Hammarby) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
Ball safe as Hammarby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the home team.
In the minute 13, Hammarby push upfield but Bojan Pandzic quickly pulls them for offside.
Throw-in for Hammarby at Tele2 Arena.
In Stockholm Hammarby attack through Gustav Ludwigson. The finish is off target, however.
In the minute 16, It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
Free kick for Hacken in the half of Hammarby.
Bojan Pandzic signals a Hacken throw-in in Hammarby's half.
In the minute 17, Hacken move into a 0-1 lead through a Alexander Soderlund header.
That's a fine assist from Ahmed Yasin.
Throw-in Hammarby.
In the minute 19, Can Hammarby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Hacken's half?
Gustav Ludwigson (Hammarby) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In the minute 20, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hacken.
Mads Fenger (Hammarby) has received a first yellow card.
Corner awarded to Hacken.
In the minute 22, Goal kick for Hammarby at Tele2 Arena.
Throw-in for Hacken close to the penalty box.
In Stockholm, Hacken push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
In the minute 25, Free kick for Hacken in their own half.
In Stockholm Hammarby drive forward through Abdul Khalili. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Corner awarded to Hammarby.
In the minute 27, Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Hacken to take a throw-in in Hammarby territory.
Bojan Pandzic awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 30, Hammarby have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Nikola Gulan for Hacken gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
Hammarby have a goal kick.
In the minute 33, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hacken in their own half.
Throw-in for Hammarby in their own half.
Gustav Ludwigson has recovered and rejoins the match in Stockholm.
Play has been temporarily suspended for attention to Erik Friberg for Hacken who is writhing in pain on the pitch.
In the minute 34, Gustav Ludwigson is down and play has been interrupted for a few moments.
Hacken's Erik Friberg is back in action after a slight knock.
In the minute 35, Free kick Hacken.
Bojan Pandzic awards Hammarby a goal kick.
Throw-in for Hammarby in the half of Hacken.
In the minute 38, Bojan Pandzic awards the away team a throw-in.
Free kick for Hammarby in the half of Hacken.
Andreas Alm (Hacken) is making a first substitution, with Adam Andersson replacing Nikola Gulan.
In the minute 41, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hacken.
Leo Bengtsson's header is off-target for Hacken.
Ball goes out of play for a Hammarby goal kick.
In the minute 43, Hacken awarded a free kick in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic signals a throw-in for Hacken, close to Hammarby's area.
Corner awarded to Hacken.
In the minute 44, Hacken's Joona Toivio goes close with his head but his effort is blocked.
Hacken have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
Free kick Hammarby.
3 minutes will be added to the 1st half in Stockholm.
Abdul Khalili of Hammarby smashes in a shot on target. The keeper saves, though.
In the minute 45, Hacken will need to be alert as they defend a dangerous free kick from Hammarby.
Goal kick for Hacken at Tele2 Arena.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 45, Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
The first half has been concluded at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 45, Ahmed Yasin (Hacken) gets a yellow card.
The second-half is underway at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 46, Ball safe as Hammarby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Free kick for Hacken in the half of Hammarby.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Stockholm.
In the minute 48, Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hacken in their own half.
Can Hacken capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Hammarby's half?
Corner awarded to Hammarby.
In the minute 52, Tim Soderstrom for Hammarby drives towards goal at Tele2 Arena. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Throw-in Hacken.
At Tele2 Arena, Hammarby are penalized for being offside.
In the minute 56, Hacken pushes forward through Rasmus Lindgren, whose finish on goal is saved.
In Stockholm a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Throw-in for Hammarby at Tele2 Arena.
In the minute 59, Hacken's Adam Andersson is on target but unsuccessful.
Hacken awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Play has been interrupted briefly in Stockholm to check on Pontus Dahlberg, who is grimacing with pain.
In the minute 63, Hacken's Pontus Dahlberg looks ok and returns to the pitch.
Free kick for Hacken in their own half.
Bojan Pandzic awards Hacken a goal kick.
In the minute 66, Throw-in for Hacken at Tele2 Arena.
Throw-in for Hammarby in their own half.
Hammarby to take a throw-in in Hacken territory.
In the minute 69, Hacken awarded a free kick in their own half.
Hacken have a goal kick.
The match has been stopped briefly for attention to the injured Richard Magyar.
In the minute 73, Richard Magyar is back on his feet again.
Throw-in high up the field for Hacken in Stockholm.
Viktor Lundberg (Hacken) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 76, Bojan Pandzic awards the home team a throw-in.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hammarby.
Alexander Soderlund (Hacken) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
In the minute 78, Hacken needs to be cautious. Hammarby have an attacking throw-in.
Ahmed Yasin gets his shot on target but fails to score for Hacken.
Hammarby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 79, Throw-in high up the field for Hammarby in Stockholm.
Ball safe as Hacken is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Throw-in for Hammarby in the half of Hacken.
In the minute 82, Throw-in Hammarby.
Bojan Pandzic signals a Hammarby throw-in in Hacken's half.
The home team have replaced Jeppe Andersen with Serge Martinsson Ngouali. This is the first substitution made today by Stefan Billborn.
In the minute 83, The away team replace Leo Bengtsson with Oskar Sverrisson.
Hacken drive upfield and Adam Andersson gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Hammarby defender.
Bojan Pandzic signals a free kick to Hacken in their own half.
Hacken's Ahmed Yasin breaks free at Tele2 Arena. But the strike goes wide of the post.
Ball goes out of play for a Hammarby goal kick.
In the minute 86, Stefan Billborn is making the team's second substitution at Tele2 Arena with Imad Khalili replacing Abdul Khalili.
In the minute 87, Free kick Hammarby.
Hacken have a goal kick.
In Stockholm Hacken drive forward through Ahmed Yasin. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Corner awarded to Hacken.
Free kick for Hammarby in their own half.
4 minutes of injury time will be added to the 2nd half.
A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
Hacken have been awarded a corner by Bojan Pandzic.
In Stockholm, Imad Khalili (Hammarby) gets his head to the ball but the strike is cleared by an untiring defence.
Free kick for Hacken in their own half.
Hammarby awarded a free kick in their own half.
It's 1-1 as the referee blows for full-time.
Tobias Carlsson is replacing Adam Andersson for Hacken at Tele2 Arena.
Aimar Sher grabs a goal to bring things level at 1-1 at Tele2 Arena.
